# Next.js App Router
- App Router only — never suggest Pages Router patterns
- Use Server Components by default; only add `'use client'` when truly needed
- Use `layout.tsx` for shared layouts, `loading.tsx` for loading states, `error.tsx` for error boundaries
- Use Route Handlers (`route.ts`) for API endpoints
- Always add proper `metadata` exports for SEO
- Use `next/image` for all images — never raw `<img>` tags
- Use `next/link` for all internal navigation
- Prefer `generateStaticParams` for static generation where possible